	 <title>System.DayOfWeek</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This operator returns an Integer from 0 to 6 representing the day of
		  the week. Sunday is 0, Monday 1, all the way to Saturday being 6.</para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select TableDee add { DateTime(2004,04,19).DayOfWeek() Day19,
                      DateTime(2004,04,24).DayOfWeek() Day24 };</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>Day19 Day24
----- -----
0     6</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
